{"word":"G1577 - ἐκκλησία - ekklēsía - ek-klay-see'-ah - Assembly","slug":"G1577","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκκλησία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ekklēsía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ek-klay-see'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Assembly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03BA;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x03C3;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B1; - ekkle&#x0304;sia</b> - <i>ek-klay-see'-ah</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1537\">G1537</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>; a <i>calling out</i>, that is, (concretely) a popular <i>meeting</i>, especially a religious <i>congregation</i> (Jewish <i>synagogue</i>, or Christian community of members on earth or saints in heaven or both): - assembly, church."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1458\">G1458</a>, <a href=\"#/G1462\">G1462</a>, <a href=\"#/G1528\">G1528</a>, <a href=\"#/G1941\">G1941</a>, <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>, <a href=\"#/G2821\">G2821</a>, <a href=\"#/G2822\">G2822</a>, <a href=\"#/G3333\">G3333</a>, <a href=\"#/G4292\">G4292</a>, <a href=\"#/G4341\">G4341</a>, <a href=\"#/G4779\">G4779</a>, <a href=\"#/G479\">G479</a>"}]}